<collectingCountry box="[662,733,980,1004]" name="China" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733">China</collectingCountry>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[801,978,980,1004]" country="China" name="Hebei" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733">Hebei Province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Mathews GB" box="[993,1172,980,1004]" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733" pagination="32 - 35" refId="ref6314" refString="Mathews GB. 1937. More tardigrades from the Far East. China Journal 27: 32 - 35." type="journal article" year="1937">Mathews 1937</bibRefCitation>
). My specimens fit the description of this species (
<bibRefCitation author="Ramazzotti G &amp; Maucci W" box="[720,1075,1012,1036]" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733" pagination="1 - 1012" refId="ref6561" refString="Ramazzotti G, Maucci W. 1983. Il Phylum Tardigrada. 3 rd ed. Memorie dell'Isituto Italiano di Idrobiologia 41: 1 - 1012. (CW Beasley, Eng translation)." type="journal article" year="1983">Ramazzotti and Maucci 1983</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Dastych H" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733" pagination="1 - 288" refId="ref5898" refString="Dastych H. 1988. The Tardigrada of Poland. Monografie Fauny Polski 16: 1 - 288." type="journal article" year="1988">Dastych 1988</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="McInnes SJ" box="[214,389,1044,1068]" pageId="15" pageNumber="2733" pagination="1419 - 1445" refId="ref6334" refString="McInnes SJ. 1995. Tardigrades from Signy Island, South Orkney Islands, with particular reference to freshwater species. Journal of Natural History 29: 1419 - 1445." type="journal article" year="1995">McInnes 1995</bibRefCitation>
). It has never been reported from Tsinling Mountains.
</paragraph>
